        {
            "title": "瀾起科技在港招股上市 籌資至多70億港元",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"瀾起科技在港招股上市 籌資至多70億港元\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"626\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/OIRfgujFni_U2aqsdRt2hA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYyNg--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-01/48b55fe0-fd81-11f0-bbfd-fb9cc5a06c5f\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">瀾起科技在港招股上市 籌資至多70億港元</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
